HEADWORD: Hagiologist
<hw>Ha`gi*ol"o*gist</hw> <pr>(-⟦osl⟧*j⟦icr⟧st)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>One who treats of the sacred writings; a writer of the lives of the
